sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Akhil)
  participant F as Frontend (Next.js)
  participant C as Amazon Cognito
  participant R as Risk Engine
  U->>F: Click "Login"
  F->>C: Redirect to Hosted UI (Auth Code + PKCE, Passkey)
  C->>F: Redirect with code
  F->>R: POST /risk/evaluate (context)
  R-->>F: allow/require_mfa
  alt High Risk
    F->>C: Redirect to MFA
  else Low/Medium
    F->>U: Show Profile
  end
